headline: Paychex Declares Quarterly Dividend
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., July 09, 2025--The Board of Directors of Paychex, Inc. (Nasdaq: PAYX) declared a regular quarterly cash dividend on Paychex common stock of $1.08 per share, payable on August 29, 2025, to shareholders of record as of July 21, 2025.
